import React from 'react'

const NavMenuClose = props => (
  <svg
    className={props.className}
    width='15'
    height='15'
    viewBox='0 0 15 15'
    fill='none'
    xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
  >
    <rect
      width='18'
      height='2'
      transform='matrix(-0.707107 0.707107 0.707107 0.707107 12.7279 0)'
      fill='white'
    />
    <rect
      x='1.5354'
      width='18'
      height='2'
      transform='rotate(45 1.5354 0)'
      fill='white'
    />
  </svg>
)

export default NavMenuClose
